Class EdgeSeed

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.operation.data.ElementSeed
      • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.operation.data.EdgeSeed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, EdgeId, ElementId
    public class EdgeSeed
extends ElementSeed
implements EdgeId
    An EdgeSeed contains source, destination and directed identifiers to identify an Edge. It is mainly used as a seed for queries.
